PLEASE NOTE: Before turning on external control in this panel, please 
ensure that you have made a valid selection for the Machine on: 
subindep_SubmitMethod.  This control is greyed out once external control 
is selected since most other controls for the specific machine are 
controlled by the SCS.

The Standard Generalised Suite control option results in additional 
changes being made to the UMUI processed output. If you are planning 
to convert the output to run with Rose, for example using Rosebud 
you should not use this option, as the changes should be the 
responsibility of the Rose conversion process. Any problems you 
encounter would need to be resolved in the Rose conversion process and 
not by relying on the Standard Generalised Suite.

If this advice causes you problems. Please contact the UMUI
team to discuss what refinements to the UMUI could help.
